description:
There are many great informative channels out there about all there is to know about flying, There are tutorials, aces showing their skills, people discussing gamedesign, issues and improvements and fun moments ingame.

This channel is none of that. There are always people who know those things better. 

The Diary is made for pilot Harry Haller, to hopefully make him learn something. But also to share those moments of fun or frustration. Are there others who struggles with the same things? Actually maybe it's the opposite of an tutorial. Please give Harry advice!

Each entry is a match or parts of a match in simulator mode. I will also try to show flight from multiple pilots perspectives to make Harry understand what's going on, and hopefully make it more interesting to watch.

/Hermine - Video Manager


Skins and other stuff here:
https://live.warthunder.com/user/Harry_Haller/

I am also a former federal uniformed police officer and former sworn deputy sheriff.  Due to my injuries, I am no longer able to perform in either career, military or law enforcement.

Physically I have disabilities, especially when it comes to lifting, pulling or pushing objects.  I have severe damage to my r-shoulder and upper spine and neck that limits me significantly in that regard. In 2018 I had my 4th major surgery in an attempt to buy me more time against losing the shoulder or attempting a replacement.  I also had two separate severe head injuries that are the most serious problem due to literal debilitating pain, 4-5 days out of each week.

description:
odos imaging is technology focused company specializing in the development and manufacture of sensor systems for the capture of high-resolution, time-of-flight, 3D video streams.

Current systems have pixel resolutions in excess of 1.3 megapixels, combined with the ability to measure both distance and intensity at each and every pixel. This unique feature provides an exact pixel-by-pixel correspondence for both distance and intensity, enabling innovative solutions to machine vision applications.

High frame rates and excellent performance in strong ambient light are key features of the technology, and allow robust operation in a wide variety of environmental conditions. Industry standard GigeVision interfaces enable rapid deployment and simple multi-system connectivity.

odos imaging offers both complete systems and component technologies for use in industrial, automation, logistics, traffic systems and numerous other demanding applications.

Hello, I'm Andy. My goal is to create entertaining videos mostly, but not only, for people who love cars & crashes. 

All the videos you'll find in this channel are recorded & edited by me and my sidekick, George, who helps with parts of the editing.
This channel is our full-time job. We're devoting a minimum of 100 hours per week to bring you the best BeamNG drive videos.

How we work:

Creating these videos is a lot harder & time consuming than you might think but it is what makes us and, hopefully, you happy!
We are playing BeamNG.drive, a PC Game featuring the ultimate soft-body physics and realism. 

The process, step by step:

- Recording the clips with Action! (10-15 hours, sometimes 15+)
- Editing & synchronizing the clips with music & addition of captions / sound effects - Premiere Pro (5-10 hours)  
- Descriptions, Thumbnails etc.  (2 hours)

We’re uploading 4 Videos per week on Tuesday, Thursday, Saturday & Sunday. Stay up to date by Subscribing!
Thank you :)

description:
My first mini album «Inner Voices Speaking» is OUT NOW🔮 These songs are my inner voices speaking - inner child, inner critic, and highest self. 

I recently found my way back to myself and to music. This led me to writing for the first time by myself! I’ve been crafting new songs and music videos, in hope to give something back to you, my patient listeners🧚🏼‍♂️ I want to thank you for sticking around all these years. I really needed to take my time. 

My biggest wish now, is that my new songs will awaken something in you... I hope they will, like my old songs, help you find the comfort and courage you need, to shine your own light❤️‍🔥

Mission Statement: To inform and advocate for the enhancement of life in the Valley.

Coverage Area: Fresno County is in the heart of the San Joaquin Valley and anchors the six-county Fresno/Visalia DMA composed of Fresno, Merced, Mariposa, Madera, Kings and Tulare counties. Fresno County's fast-growing population -- nearly 950,000 in 2012 -- is one of the most diverse in the nation.

Circulation Area: The Fresno Bee's circulation area covers approximately 18,000 square miles. For 15 consecutive years, The Bee has ranked first in penetration of its Newspaper Designated Market among all California newspapers with more than 100,000 circulation.

Customers: Each week, The Fresno Bee's print and online products reach 68% of adults in Fresno County.

description:
This 'Channel' is, mostly, about documenting Trains. No music, No narration, just the sight and sound of trains. Locations are around the Southern Interior, the Greater Vancouver, Fraser Valley & Fraser Canyon areas of British Columbia, Canada.
I record trains in UHD video and stereo sound. I am neither a Foamer nor hardly even a real Railfan, (and there is nothing wrong with being either!). I can't identify trains  on sight. But as a retired investigator, researcher & analyst, I know how & where to look. 
Equipment used includes a Canon XA55 4K UHD in 1920x1080 with an external Azden SMX-10 microphone housed in a Rode Blimp, and a Neewer 7" field monitor.  Video is edited and produced using Cyberlink PowerDirector. I try to use a tripod at all times.  Ego servabo conatur

description:
MIKROTRON - a brand of SVS-Vistek GmbH

The MIKROTRON brand is internationally known in the machine vision market for small, particularly robust High-Speed cameras that are used in industrial and scientific applications as well as in sports, advertising and nature filming.

SVS-Vistek GmbH has exceptional know-how in industrial image processing as an innovative manufacturer of high-quality industrial CCD and CMOS cameras for more than 35 years. 
We develop and produce a wide range of standard cameras as well as cameras with the highest resolutions and highest speeds, above-average image quality and all relevant interfaces in our own clean rooms at our headquarters in Gilching near Munich: Quality Made in Germany! 
With subsidiaries in the USA and Japan as well as a large partner network, we can advise, support and serve customers of many markets worldwide.

So here is where you'll find me getting my tech fix, you'll find videos on Quantel's products, electronics, teardowns of old scientific equipment or other unusual items, geiger counters and occasionally fixing things.

Located in Manchester, United Kingdom. In my youth i would take just about everything i could find to bits, some of it went back together some didn't. I just had a intense desire to see what was inside and find out how it works.

Sadly i didn't pursue electronics and favoured computing instead, cutting my teeth on the Spectrum, Atari ST, Falcon030, TT030 and the PC too and went on to design websites in the 1990s, hand coding html and eventually web application development and also administering front and back end servers for a multinational company (now long gone!). So my understanding of electronics is at a basic hobbyist level though i love reading and learning about things i don't know.

Military service Robinson served as a rifleman in World War I with New York's 15th Infantry Regiment, National Guard. The Regiment was renamed the 369th Infantry while serving under France's Fourth Army and earned the nickname the "Harlem Hellfighters".

According to his biographer, Robinson had previously served in the Spanish–American War, where he sustained an accidental gunshot wound, was 40 when the U.S entered World War I, and received a letter of commendation from the War Department for his work during the war in boosting morale at training camps in the United States, not overseas.[4]:p. 98

Along with serving in the trenches in World War I, Robinson was also the 369th "Hellfighters Band" drum major and led the regimental band up Fifth Avenue on the 369th's return from overseas.[24]

description:
Hallo an alle!

Mein Name ist Robin und ich freue mich, dass ihr euch durch den Kanal klickt!
Kurz zu meiner Person: Ich bin 32 Jahre alt und habe einen Master-Abschluss im Bereich Maschinenbau. In verschiedenen technischen und naturwissenschaftlichen Bereichen gibt es wöchentlich ein Video.

Neben aktuellen Ereignissen, greife ich diverse interessante oder wissenswerte Themen auf und arbeite diese in Videos auf. Die Chemie-Versuche führe ich zusammen mit einem guten Freund durch, der durch seine Ausbildung diese durchführen darf.

Für Ideen oder Vorschläge bitte einfach eine Nachricht schreiben oder ein Kommentar posten. Für Anfragen gerne auch meine Email-Adresse verwenden.
Ich wünsche ganz viel Spaß mit den Videos!

Falls Interesse an der Verwendung meiner Videos besteht, bitte anfragen. Danke :)

description:
Platinum-selling rapper Herbert “G Herbo” Wright has endured a season of close calls and losing several of his closest friends to senseless gun violence in his native Chicago. All of this was channeled into his critically acclaimed double album, Survivor’s Remorse in 2022 which Rolling Stone called, “another potent look into his rattled, conflicted psyche that also doubles as a celebration of his 10-year run as one of the most enduring young rappers to come out of Chicago’s drill scene.” Following up from his 2023 mixtape, Strictly For My Fans 2, and earning  Platinum and Gold plaques for Nardo Wick’s “Who Want Smoke” and his late friend Young Dolph’s “One Scale” that same year, Herbo aims to reach his full potential as an artist with his celebratory offering for the summertime, Big Swerv. The album is executive produced by longtime collaborators Southside and Big Oz.
G Herbo's four albums,”PTSD,” “25,” “Swervo,” and his debut, “Humble Beast” all reached the Billboard Top 200 chart.

description:
We are two sisters on a mission to demystify science with humor and relevance by creating videos, GIFs, comics, and resources. Our content is focused on high school biology (Pinky is a former high school biology teacher), though we do receive comments that some of our content is useful for intro biology courses at the college level as well. We're for anyone wanting to learn biology!

We frequently remind viewers that we cannot include all of the fascinating exceptions and details in a video under 10 minutes. We like to create memorable visuals to the content, but they're not scientific illustrations. Meaning, nitrogen and carbon don't tap dance. Our illustrated cell and molecule cartoons are definitely not to scale.  DNA is usually a right-handed double helix (well...there are exceptions) and it doesn't have eyes...a face...or a top hat...

description:
The HACO Group: more than just sheet metal

HACO started in 1965 as a small Flemish family-owned business serving local industrial companies.  Today, we are more and more a group offering a full range of high-quality solutions, which are known around the globe. From professional woodworking, sheet metal working, and aluminum milling machines to machine controls and surfacing installations. 

Originally famous for our sheet metal and woodworking machines, HACO has become so much more than just a manufacturer of punching machines, bending machines and shears. Since the mid-nineties, HACO has evolved into a company that produces not only sheet metal machines, but also larger and more complex machines, like machining centers and turning machines.

description:
Former NASA engineer. Current CrunchLabs founder and friend of science.

Answers to some common questions:

1) I make a monthly toy we build together on a video, that gets delivered to your house that teaches you to think like an engineer.  Check it out at- https://crunchlabs.com
2) I studied Mechanical Engineering in School.  I did my undergrad at BYU and Masters at USC.
3) I worked for NASA JPL for 9 years, 7 of which were working on the Curiosity Rover (I made a video about it you should def totes watch cause it's probably my favorite of all my videos).  Then I made some Halloween costumes.  Then I worked for Apple in their Special Projects Group doing Product Design as a Mechanical Engineer for 5 years. Then in 2022 I created CrunchLabs to deliver monthly toys that teach you to think like an engineer.

description: The folks at Periscope Film have been rescuing and preserving one film at a time -- and making them available to the public for free on YouTube -- for over a decade. Our rates are competitive and affordable, because we work with clients to meet their needs.  And because we scan actual motion picture prints, we can deliver everything you need in 24p High Definition HD and 2k/4k. Want to support our activities and help us preserve more rare films? description:
High Speed Interconnects (HSI) is an American company, which extrudes and assembles high-performance coaxial cable assemblies to meet your challenging electrical and mechanical requirements. HSI's low-loss, low-capacitance, phase-stable coaxial interconnect solutions are available in a variety of cable constructions including circular and micro coaxial connector terminations down to 0.3mm pitch and fine wire direct to board terminations down to 0.175 mm

Headquartered in Scottsdale, AZ, HSI is one of a few global manufacturers extruding its own high-performance coaxial cable and expanded PTFE. HSI's coaxial cable assemblies range from 16 to 52 AWG and are available in a variety of configurations such as; single coax, twinax, triax, quadax, shielded parallel pairs, shielded twisted pairs, differential pairs, and other multi-conductor solutions. HSI's assemblies are available as discrete, ribbonized, or multiconductor (bundled) constructions.

description:
Everybody has Socialist values until someone tells them their values are called Socialist.

What does left mean?
In politics, left refers to people and groups that have liberal views. That generally means they support progressive reforms, especially those seeking greater social and economic equality.
The far left is often used for what is considered more extreme, revolutionary views, such as communism and socialism. Collectively, people and groups, are referred to as the Left or the left wing.

What does right mean?
The word right, in contrast, refers to people or groups that have conservative views. That generally means they are disposed to preserving existing conditions and institutions. 
The far right is often used for more extreme, nationalistic viewpoints, including fascism and some oppressive ideologies. People and groups,  are collectively referred to as the Right or the right wing.

description:
TopPop was the first regular dedicated pop music TV show in the Dutch language area. Dutch broadcaster AVRO aired the programme weekly, from 1970 to 1988. 
Presenter Ad Visser hosted the show for its first fifteen years.
World famous music artists performed on TopPop: ABBA, 10CC, Bee Gees, The Jacksons, David Bowie, Earth & Fire, Boney M, Queen, Golden Earring, KC & The Sunshine Band, Chic and many more!

LICENSING
For licensing inquiries please contact toppop@avrotros.nl 

AVROTROS is a Dutch radio and television broadcaster, founded in 2014 from a merger of AVRO and TROS. From January 1st, 2014 the name of the merged broadcaster was used in joint programmes. AVRO was founded in 1923 as the Netherlands first public broadcaster. TROS started broadcasting in 1964. Toppop was a weekly AVRO pop program that was aired between 1970 and 1988.
